lead_paragraph: For $9,600, fans of former U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Clinton can rent a luxury suite for her scheduled June speech near Denver, part of a package that includes seats for 26 guests and five VIP parking passes.

headline.main: Ticket Sales Brisk for Hillary Clinton's Speaking Tour
